snippet.title: Best VGM 2062 - Phoenix Wright : Trials and Tribulations - Fragrance of Dark Coffee
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 2288 - https://youtu.be/wDPyjioLDrw

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo DS
Phoenix Wright Ace Attorney: Trials and Tribulations (2004)
Fragrance of Dark Coffee
Noriyuki Iwadare
